 {"id":"a2rchitech-65r","title":"Add Integration and E2E Tests for Polish Features","description":"---\n## 📋 MANDATORY PRE-REQUISITE READING\nBefore starting work on this issue, you MUST read these law files (located in ../Architecture/LAW/):\n\n1. **Project_Law.md**\n   - LAW-ORG-001: PRD-First Development\n   - LAW-ORG-003: Context Reset Discipline\n   - LAW-ENF-001: Mandatory Load Order\n   - LAW-META-004: Deterministic Loop\n\n2. **Guardrails.md**\n   - Section 2: Mandatory Planning Guardrail (Plan Before Action)\n   - Section 3: Separation of Phases (Planning ≠ Execution)\n   - Section 5: Static Safety Guardrails (No Rule Disabling)\n\n3. **RepoLaw.md**\n   - A1. PRD-First Development (INTENT ANCHOR)\n   - A4. Context Reset (SESSION BOUNDARY LAW)\n   - A5. System Evolution Mindset (COMPOUNDING LAW)\n\n## Required Planning Phase (Per Guardrails.md)\nBefore executing any code changes, you MUST produce a structured plan following this template:\n\n**PLAN**\n- Goal: [1-2 sentences]\n- Non-Goals: [What you will NOT do]\n- Constraints: [Limitations and boundaries]\n- Affected Modules / Files: [List]\n- Structural Changes: [Description]\n- Breaking Changes: [Yes/No]\n- Tests Required: [Yes/No and what kind]\n- Rollback Strategy: [If applicable]\n\nExecution without an approved plan is **invalid output** per Guardrails.md Section 2.\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nValidates polish features with experience-level tests covering all 3 interaction loops and capsule switching behavior.\n\n## Tasks\n\n### Test Loop A: Evidence Accumulation\n**File**: `tests/e2e/evidence-accumulation.spec.ts`\n\n1. Add 3 evidence items\n   - Input: URLs for vegan restaurant list, museum hours, weather forecast\n   - Expected: 3 evidence cards appear in Evidence Rail\n   - States: loading → ready (shimmer → settled)\n   - Verify: Each card shows favicon, title, badges (kind, freshness, confidence)\n2. Toggle pin/exclude states\n   - Click pin toggle → state changes to pinned\n   - Click exclude → card dims/removes\n   - Expected: State is persisted\n\n### Test Loop B: Synthesis Moment\n**File**: `tests/e2e/synthesis-transition.spec.ts`\n\n1. Click Synthesize button\n   - Precondition: 2+ evidence items exist\n   - Action: Click \"Synthesize\" CTA\n   - Expected:\n     - Evidence cards slide inward (200-400ms)\n     - Canvas fades in (opacity: 0 → 1, 300ms)\n     - Canvas scales up (scale 0.98 → 1.0, 200ms)\n     - Toast appears: \"Created [Capsule Name]\"\n     - Toast has undo button\n2. Test undo functionality\n   - Click toast undo button\n   - Expected:\n     - Toast dismisses\n     - Canvas removes\n     - Evidence rail returns to pre-synthesis state\n\n### Test Loop C: Iterative Updates\n**File**: `tests/e2e/iterative-updates.spec.ts`\n\n1. Add evidence after synthesis\n   - Precondition: Capsule is active (canvas visible)\n   - Action: Add 1 new evidence URL\n   - Expected:\n     - Update banner slides down: \"Updated [Section]: +1 items (ev_id)\"\n     - Canvas updates without full wipe\n     - Scroll position preserved\n     - Input focus maintained\n2. Test \"Why updated?\" panel\n   - Click update banner\n   - Expected: DiffPanel opens with change summary\n   - Verify: Human-readable message (not raw JSON)\n   - Verify: Evidence ID links are clickable\n   - Click diff entry\n   - Expected: Corresponding section in canvas flashes (highlight animation)\n\n### Test Capsule Switching\n**File**: `tests/e2e/capsule-switching.spec.ts`\n\n1. Create 2 capsules\n   - Create \"Trip Planner\" capsule\n   - Create \"Research Synthesis\" capsule\n   - Expected: Both appear in TabBar/Capsule Dock\n2. Switch between capsules\n   - Click TabBar item for capsule A\n   - Expected: Canvas slides horizontally (like app switch, not page reload)\n   - Click TabBar item for capsule B\n   - Expected: Canvas slides back, content updates\n   - Verify: No full page reload visible\n   - Verify: Each capsule maintains its scroll position\n\n### Test Responsive Behavior\n**File**: `tests/e2e/responsive-layout.spec.ts`\n\n1. Desktop viewport (1024px+)\n   - Expected: 3-pane layout visible\n   - Evidence Rail: Left, 250px\n   - Canvas: Center, flex\n   - Action Dock: Right, 280px\n2. Mobile viewport (375px)\n   - Expected:\n     - Evidence Rail hidden (drawer)\n     - Action Dock hidden (sheet)\n     - Canvas takes full width\n3. Toggle mobile drawer\n   - Click drawer toggle button\n   - Expected: Evidence Rail slides up from bottom\n   - Swipe down or click outside → drawer closes\n4. Toggle mobile sheet\n   - Click sheet toggle\n   - Expected: Action Dock slides down from top\n   - Click outside or close button → sheet dismisses\n\n## Integration Tests\n**File**: `apps/ui/src/a2ui/polish-features.test.ts`\n\n1. Test component rendering\n   - SplitPane: Renders 3 panes correctly\n   - EvidenceCard: Shows all metadata\n   - Toast: Renders and dismisses\n   - Chip: Displays token with correct color\n   - DiffPanel: Shows journal events\n\n2. Test state management\n   - UIState extensions work correctly\n   - Toast queue manages multiple toasts\n   - Journal events trigger updates\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- 5 E2E test files (one per acceptance criteria)\n- 1 integration test file for new components\n- Playwright test configuration updated\n- All tests passing (`npm run test:all`)\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n- All 5 acceptance tests pass\n- Evidence accumulation test validates card states\n- Synthesis transition test validates animation sequence\n- Iterative update test validates banner + diff panel\n- Capsule switching test validates app-like feel\n- Responsive test validates mobile drawer/sheet behavior\n- Integration tests validate component rendering\n\n---\n\nSpec Reference: UNIFIED_UI_IMPLEMENTATION.md - Acceptance Tests, Motion Grammar\nBlocking: a2rchitech-7dm (Layout Foundation), a2rchitech-554 (Synthesis Transitions), a2rchitech-m1y (Iterative Updates), a2rchitech-fa5 (Goal Tokens)\n","status":"in_progress","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-11T13:36:43.587744-06:00","created_by":"macbook","updated_at":"2026-01-11T16:13:06.988443-06:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"a2rchitech-65r","depends_on_id":"a2rchitech-7dm","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-11T13:37:04.630811-06:00","created_by":"daemon"},{"issue_id":"a2rchitech-65r","depends_on_id":"a2rchitech-554","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-11T13:37:04.674749-06:00","created_by":"daemon"},{"issue_id":"a2rchitech-65r","depends_on_id":"a2rchitech-m1y","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-11T13:37:04.720477-06:00","created_by":"daemon"},{"issue_id":"a2rchitech-65r","depends_on_id":"a2rchitech-fa5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-11T13:37:04.765401-06:00","created_by":"daemon"}]}
